  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Transforming Lives through Education Rural Oaxaca</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In a traditional indigenous, Zapotec village, where schools and teachers do not typically have the energy to dedicate one on one time with the children, understanding the needs of each child and how to best support them, Ananda Learning Center offers alternative, holistic, nature based, &quot;private&quot; school education at public school costs. We also offer trainings to public school teachers and directors so that Montessori and other alternative methodologies do not need to be so inaccessible.</narrative>
  </description>
